<p>Our BMR calculation tool is based on formulas and scientific principles that are backed by well-known health and nutrition experts. They are leaders in their respective fields, offering years of knowledge and experience.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Our calculator considers factors such as weight, height, gender, and age. This provides a more accurate output estimation that can be used to determine energy needs.&nbsp;</p>



